### **2. 37_EndpointWaveGrid**  
**Description:**  
Scans and tracks the behavior of multiple API endpoints, detecting latency waves and downtime blips.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# EndpointWaveGrid - API Latency Monitor

EndpointWaveGrid gives developers a real-time view of endpoint response behavior across clusters or regions.

## Features
- Status + latency snapshot  
- Wave/burst visualization  
- CSV / JSON output  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/37_EndpointWaveGrid.git
cd 37_EndpointWaveGrid
python monitor.py
